parameters.content:
## Update 4 tenant forms' email autocompletion text box parameter
** 4 forms including: notice to vacate, maintenance, entry condition report, exit condition report
## Update application form's "which room you are applying for" options parameter

## Trigger Events For updating Jotform parameters
** new renter move in (new lease created) - update both current_renter_emails and for_rent_listings
** renter intend to move out (new notice to vacate received) - update for_rent_listings
** renter moved out (user type changed from tenant to past tenant ) - update current_renter_emails
** renter email updated (user table's email column is updated) - update current_renter_emails

Available  
 Cleaning of Common Area Every 4 - 6 weeks! 
 Follows Legal Procedures! 

 Flat Details:
3-bedroom, 1-bathroom flat in Melbourne CBD
Right across from Flinders Street Station & Federation Square. It's within the Free Tram Zone 
Your own private room with basic furniture 
Share the common area with 2 other awesome flatmates from around the world  (max 3 people)

 Rental Process:
 Bond deposit handled with RTBA
 Residential Tenancy Agreement signing
 Video condition reports before move-in and upon move-out for smooth tenancy

 Friendly Environment: 
  Landlord does not live in the flat 
  Current tenants are super nice and get along well 

 Note:
Quilts and covers in pictures are for demo purposes; bring your own if you prefer, but we can provide them if needed

 Included:
 FREE WiFi 
 Common area appliances, cookware, etc. 
 Bills (electricity, water, gas) split evenly among tenants (approx. AUD 5 - 10 per week per pax)

 Room AUMF08-2:
 Weekly Rent: A$225 (14-weeks minimum)
 Unique room made from large Lego blocks  (not fully soundproof but offers privacy)
 Furnished with Single Bedframe, Single Mattress, Lock on bedroom door, Desk, Chair, Desk Lamp, Bedside Lamp, Socket * 2, Quilt, Pillows * 2, Bedsheet + Duvet Cover Set, Bedspread, Cushion * 1, Keys&Cards: 1 CardUnique room made from large Lego blocks  (not fully soundproof but offers privacy)

 For More Info:
Check out details about the neighborhood, amenities, and flatmates on our website:https://roomly.com.au/products/aumf08-2
 Contact Us:
Interested? SMS or whatsapp Message us at 0428083889 to grab your spot in this awesome flat (calls are not available)!
